Fortis Prime Fund Solutions is a new service platform which draws on the global strengths of Fortis. We are the sole provider of an integrated package of services to hedge funds and funds-of-funds. Such products are unrelated to brokerage and research thereby enabling Fortis to work as a strategic partner with its clients in offering unbiased service and advice. Through its extensive experience with offshore activities, including comprehensive fund administration, financing of trade positions, clearing transactions, safekeeping of portfolios and covering of short sales, Fortis offers a “one-stop-shop” for all of a fund’s administrative and financing needs. Alternatively, clients may choose selective services which are complementary to their existing servicing structure. Fortis has considerable expertise in providing professional assistance with the establishment and set-up of new funds and structures domiciled in both common law and civil law jurisdictions. Fortis’ clients use all types of fund structures, in every time zone, in every type of jurisdiction, both on- and offshore. Through its international banking network, Fortis also offers its clients access to a full range of treasury and banking services (including cash management facilities, currency overlay and ad hoc financial solutions) and global custody (including the added-value services of securities lending and equity financing). Globally, Fortis administers over 1,400 funds with net assets in excess of US$100 billion, from six key offshore locations: Cayman Islands, Curacao, Hong Kong, Ireland, Isle of Man and Luxembourg. In addition, it has representative offices in Amsterdam, London, New York and Tokyo.

