 Environmental, Social and Corporate GovernanceAt Man Group, we believe that responsible investing is fundamental to fulfilling our fiduciary duty. Learn more about what we are doing in the area of responsible and ESG investing.
FRM Early View June 2017June was a mixed month for hedge fund returns, with Equity Long-Short and Relative Value strategies generally performing well on increased single security alpha, while Credit and Global Macro struggled.
Man Booker PrizeThe longlist, or ‘Man Booker Dozen’, for the £50,000 Man Booker Prize was announced Thursday 27 July 2017.


Man GPM AaltoMan GPM Aalto (‘Aalto’) forms the real assets business of Man GPM. Aalto is a real asset investment manager offering differentiated debt and equity strategies in commercial and residential real estate. 
Join the Man Group teamWe pride ourselves on the quality of our people; joining Man Group means becoming part of a high calibre team.
PerspectivesAt Man Group, we believe that different investment styles and approaches can be effective and beneficial to each other as we challenge consensus and convention.
AHL ExplainsNarrated by Man AHL's Chief Scientist, Dr Anthony Ledford, the ‘AHL Explains’ video series explores key concepts in futures trend following programmes – bringing each concept to life by focusing on principles, not details.































